OL,3,CMan posted antisemitic message hours
OL,4,Cafter synagogue terror attack
OL,6,FA man has been sentenced after posting
OL,7,Fa hateful antisemitic message on
OL,8,Fsocial media shortly after a deadly
OL,9,Fterrorist attack on a Manchester
OL,10,Fsynagogue.
OL,12,FAiden Stanley, 20, from Manchester,
OL,13,Fposted a message on social media
OL,14,Fwithin hours of the Heaton Park
OL,15,Fattack, using emojis including a sword
OL,16,Fand commenting: "should have been me
OL,17,Fwho done it".
