OL,3,CMan posted antisemitic message hours
OL,4,Cafter synagogue terror attack
OL,6,FHe was sentenced to an 18 month
OL,7,Fcommunity order with 20 rehabilitation
OL,8,Fdays and a #160 fine. The sentence
OL,9,Fincluded an uplift to mark the hate
OL,10,Felement of the offence.
OL,12,FPeter Conroy, District Crown
OL,13,FProsecutor at the Crown Prosecution
OL,14,FService, said, "Aiden Stanley
OL,15,Fknowingly posted a grossly offensive,
OL,16,Fantisemitic message on social media.
OL,18,F"The timing of the post, within just
OL,19,Fsix hours of the devastating synagogue
OL,20,Fattack in which two people died, makes
OL,21,Fit all the more disturbing."
