OL,3,CMan posted antisemitic message hours
OL,4,Cafter synagogue terror attack
OL,6,FHe added, "Stanley wanted to provoke a
OL,7,Fcommunity who had already faced
OL,8,Fenormous suffering, and his sickening
OL,9,Factions were made all the worse by the
OL,10,Ffact many were mourning the loss of
OL,11,Ffamily and friends following this
OL,12,Fterror attack.
OL,14,F"There is no place for hate in our
OL,15,Fsociety and we will continue to work
OL,16,Fwith partners to bring those who
OL,17,Fspread hate in our communities to
OL,18,Fjustice."
OL,20,FStanley's post was reported to police
OL,21,Fand he was arrested on 3 October 2025.
