OL,3,CMan posted antisemitic message hours
OL,4,Cafter synagogue terror attack
OL,6,FDuring his police interview he
OL,7,Fadmitted the post was about Jewish
OL,8,Fpeople and claimed he had done it to
OL,9,Fimpress people who would think it was
OL,10,Ffunny.
OL,12,FWhen faced with then evidence, on 6
OL,13,FOctober 2025 he pleaded guilty to a
OL,14,Fcharge of sending a grossly offensive
OL,15,Fmessage.
OL,17,FHe was sentenced this morning (29
OL,18,FJanuary 2026) at Manchester City
OL,19,FMagistrates' Court.
