OL,3,CMan posted antisemitic message hours
OL,4,Cafter synagogue terror attack
OL,6,FThe Community Security Trust (CST),
OL,7,Fthe charity that protects British Jews
OL,8,Ffrom terrorism and antisemitism,
OL,9,Fdescribed Stanley's post as "malicious
OL,10,Fand deeply disturbing."
OL,12,FIn a statement, they said, "At a
OL,13,Fmoment of shock and grief, his actions
OL,14,Fwere callous and deliberate,
OL,15,Famplifying an already heightened sense
OL,16,Fof fear.
OL,18,F"This prosecution demonstrates that
OL,19,Fthose who seek to exploit acts of
OL,20,Fterrorism to intimidate or incite
OL,21,Fhatred will be held to account."
